BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF OHIO:
Section 1. That sections 341.193, 753.022, and 5120.052 of 7
the Revised Code be enacted to read as follows: 8
Sec. 341.193. (A) As used in this section : 9
(1) "County correctional facility" means a county jail, 10
county workhouse, minimum security jail, joint city and county 11
workhouse, municipal-county correctional center, multicounty- 12
municipal correctional center, municipal-county jail or 13
workhouse, or multicounty-municipal jail or workhouse. 14
(2) "Teletypewriter" or "TTY" means a communication device 15
used by people who are deaf, hard of hearing, or have severe 16
speech impairment. 17
(B) Each county correctional facility shall provide every 18
inmate who is deaf, hard of hearing, or severely speech impaired 19

